OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774026671
OL,3,CDog owners warned to keep pets away
OL,4,Cfrom daffodils, tulips and bluebells
OL,6,FThe charity Dogs Trust is reminding
OL,7,Fowners of the hazards some spring
OL,8,Fplants can pose risks to dogs.
OL,10,FDaffodils, tulips and bluebells can be
OL,11,Ftoxic, causing symptoms from vomiting
OL,12,Fand lethargy to seizures in severe
OL,13,Fcases.
OL,15,FOwners should contact a vet
OL,16,Fimmediately if ingestion is suspected,
OL,17,Feven if symptoms aren't yet visible.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
