FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774026671
OL,3,CDog owners warned to keep pets away
OL,4,Cfrom daffodils, tulips and bluebells
OL,6,FCommon signs of poisoning may include
OL,7,Fvomiting, diarrhoea, excessive
OL,8,Fdrooling, lethargy, and, in severe
OL,9,Fcases, difficulty breathing, tremors,
OL,10,Fand even seizures.
OL,12,FIn some cases, spring bulb poisoning
OL,13,Fcan prove fatal.
OL,15,FAideen OConnor, Senior Veterinary
OL,16,FSurgeon at Dogs Trust, says: "After
OL,17,Fwhat feels like an incredibly long
OL,18,Fwinter, it's wonderful to see the
OL,19,Fearly signs of spring popping up
OL,20,Fthrough the ground.
OL,26,@xD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
